                  "body": {
                    "type": "TextualBody",
                    "value": "\n                              <p rend=\"align(right)\">\n                                        <placeName>New York</placeName>\n                                        <date>March 28 1851</date>\n                              </p>\n                              <p>\n                                        <sic>\n                                                  <addressee>Mr. I. Lesser</addressee>\n                                        </sic>\n                              </p>\n                              <p rend=\"indent(1)\">Dear Sir</p>\n                              <p>As I am residing now here, you<lb/> will in future not send that\n                                        Book<lb/> to <placeName>Edgefield U. S. C.</placeName> but\n                                        send<lb/> me my a/c to <placeName>180 &amp; 182 corner\n                                                  Centre &amp; <del>Stret</del><lb/>\n                                                  Hester</placeName>, to <persName>Pecan &amp;\n                                                  Smith</persName>. I will<lb/> send you the money\n                                        to <placeName>Pha.</placeName> or should<lb/> I come on\n                                                  <sic>their</sic> before you send it<lb/> I will\n                                        call on you and pay it. I<lb/> remain Very Resp Yours</p>\n                              <p rend=\"indent(2)\">\n                                        <persName role=\"author\">\n                                                  <hi rend=\"underline\">I. Cohn</hi>\n                                        </persName>\n                              </p>\n                              <p>P.S. I bought of you a few years<lb/> ago a new sett of Prayer\n                                        books<lb/> but my Shabbath book got lost<lb/> it was full\n                                        bound. If you will send<lb/> one with the Bill you shall\n                                        recd<lb/> pay in full. If my Year<lb/> of Subscription is\n                                        out I wish you<lb/> would not send any more</p>\n                              "
                  },
                  "target": "https://colenda.library.upenn.edu/items/ark:/81431/p3n010d52/canvas/p1"
                }
              ]
            }
